title: Neon Green Icons Pack - ADW GO
creator: DroidAhead

extendedInfo.description: Neon Green Icons Pack for Launch-X, ADW Launcher EX, Go Launcher EX and LauncherPro.This icons pack includes over 350 HD icons compatible with:* Launch-X (both FREE and Pro versions)* ADW Launcher EX* GO Launcher EX* LauncherPro (both FREE and Plus versions)The icons pack is compatible also with Honeycomb and Ice Cream Sandwich (ICS) devices.** HOW TO USE WITH: ***** LAUNCH-X **** APPLY ICONS PACK *- Open Launch-X- Select an existing widget (or create a new one)- Select 'Appearance Options'- Scroll to the bottom- Click on 'Icons Pack'- Select your desired theme/icons pack* APPLY SINGLE ICON *- Open Launch-X- Select an existing widget- Click on 'Select widget items'- Click on the item you'd like to change the icon- Select 'Custom icon'- Select 'Theme Icons Packs'- Select your desired theme/icons pack- Choose your custom icon*** ADW LAUNCHER **** APPLY ICONS PACK *- Go to your homescreen- Press menu and select 'ADWSettings'- Select 'Themes Preferences'- Under 'Icons' press 'Choose...'- Select your desired theme/icons pack* APPLY SINGLE ICON *- Long-press an item (app/shortcut)- Select 'Edit'- Press the icon button- Choose 'ADWTheme IconPacks'- Select your desired theme/icons pack- Choose your custom icon*** GO LAUNCHER **** APPLY ICONS PACK *- Go to your homescreen- Press menu and select 'Themes'- Press the 'Setting' button- Select 'Icons'- Select 'Theme icon'- Select your desired theme/icons pack* APPLY SINGLE ICON *- Long-press an item (app/shortcut)- Click on 'Replace'- Select 'Theme's icon'- Change the 'Selected theme'- Select your desired theme/icons pack- Choose your custom icon*** LAUNCHERPRO **** APPLY ICONS PACK *- Go to your homescreen- Press menu and select 'Preferences'- Select 'Theme Settings'- Click on 'Icon Pack'- Select your desired theme/icons packTo request new icons simply send us an email to support [at] droidahead [dot] com.

reviews.title: Amazing icons
reviews.comment: Wow some of the best icons I\'ve seen and there is tons of icons and the best part it\'s free. Oh I know what you guys should do a neon red theme please that would be friggin sweet. Please add some more icons please!!!!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Fix please
reviews.comment: The screen closes before I can look at icons. I like the color, but it would be nice if I can look at the icons for longer than 1 second.
reviews.author: stacey ferrel

reviews.title: Awesome
reviews.comment: HD graphics very well done, 3D. I\'m very impressed though kind of bitter the developer didn\'t put a FRACTION of this skill into the purple. They\'re all washed out and blurry... instead of sharp & HD violet. Also... where is the PINK theme!? I\'d pay $2.99 for that!
reviews.author: lyndsey darwin

reviews.title: Switched to Smart Launcher
reviews.comment: Taking these with me, I love these & the purple set . Very happy they\'re compatible, don\'t want to lose them .
reviews.author: Char G

reviews.title: I LOVE THE ICONS
reviews.comment: I love green. Thanks for the icons
